WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.940
=Episode 8=

01:38.570 --> 01:40.490
Duan Jiuxiu, Elder Tianji

01:41.210 --> 01:42.850
was already killed by my aunt.

01:43.980 --> 01:44.820
Uncle Zhou,

01:46.180 --> 01:47.850
why is he still alive?

01:49.930 --> 01:50.770
Zhizhen,

01:51.770 --> 01:52.610
are you all right?

01:52.621 --> 01:54.462
(Young Zhou Zhizhen, Peiqiong Manor)
I'm fine.

01:54.473 --> 01:55.210
Pingshu is injured.

01:55.260 --> 01:56.894
(Young Zhou Zhiqin)
I'll escort her back.

01:58.410 --> 01:59.250
Be careful.

02:00.020 --> 02:00.860
Goodbye.

02:06.690 --> 02:07.820
Look carefully.

02:08.290 --> 02:09.220
Leave no one alive.

02:09.570 --> 02:10.410
Yes.

02:21.540 --> 02:22.820
I have

02:23.060 --> 02:24.980
the Ziwei Method.

02:30.610 --> 02:32.260
I am a member of the Six Sects.

02:32.850 --> 02:35.290
How could I collude
with the demonic sect?

02:35.540 --> 02:37.170
Elder Tianji has long been dead.

02:37.410 --> 02:38.290
Zhao,

02:38.290 --> 02:39.820
don't listen to his slander.

02:39.820 --> 02:41.260
At a time like this,

02:41.260 --> 02:43.340
what is there left to hide?

02:43.340 --> 02:45.380
When you and Elder Tianji came to me,

02:45.380 --> 02:47.100
you said that with the Ziwei Method,

02:47.100 --> 02:49.850
we wouldn't have to be
anyone's lackey anymore

02:49.850 --> 02:51.730
or do dirty, exhausting work.

02:51.730 --> 02:53.890
You even said
that Zhou Zhizhen wasn't better

02:53.890 --> 02:56.540
than you in fighting or capability,

02:56.660 --> 02:58.980
so why couldn't you become the lord?

02:59.220 --> 03:00.060
You said

03:00.060 --> 03:01.290
you'd unify

03:01.290 --> 03:02.660
the Six Sects soon.

03:02.660 --> 03:03.500
Shut up.

03:04.010 --> 03:04.850
Mr. Zhou,

03:05.540 --> 03:06.890
you're so foolish.

03:07.290 --> 03:09.850
Why would Elder Tianji pass
his martial arts to you?

03:09.850 --> 03:12.243
If not to rope you in as an inside man
among the Six Sects,

03:12.340 --> 03:13.410
that old jerk

03:14.340 --> 03:15.500
would never have survived

03:15.660 --> 03:17.690
in the Li Sect.

03:17.980 --> 03:20.010
How could he cultivate the Ziwei Method?

03:20.610 --> 03:21.730
Once I leave,

03:22.130 --> 03:23.940
I will surely report to the Chief.

03:33.010 --> 03:34.290
Cowardly scoundrel.

03:34.780 --> 03:36.060
Sowing discord.

03:36.290 --> 03:37.130
Master,

03:38.220 --> 03:40.060
didn't we agree to practice in secret?

03:40.290 --> 03:41.730
If you report to the Chief,

03:42.660 --> 03:44.340
we won't be able to practice anymore.

03:46.220 --> 03:48.540
Uncle Jiu knew you harbored
ulterior motives.

03:48.540 --> 03:49.679
He had me keep an eye on you.

03:49.690 --> 03:51.540
You really thought I fancied you

03:51.660 --> 03:53.660
and was willing to be your deputy?

03:54.060 --> 03:54.900
You...

04:01.850 --> 04:02.690
Zhao,

04:03.380 --> 04:04.820
hand over the saliva.

04:05.100 --> 04:07.780
Our sects have been friends
for generations.

04:07.780 --> 04:09.410
You are also about to marry Yuqi.

04:09.690 --> 04:11.060
We will be family.

04:11.260 --> 04:12.100
Now,

04:12.660 --> 04:13.850
I've lost my son.

04:13.980 --> 04:15.780
You and Yuqi are my children.

04:15.780 --> 04:17.660
We can cultivate
the Ziwei Method together

04:17.660 --> 04:19.540
and bring glory to our sects.

04:19.700 --> 04:20.540
That way,

04:21.100 --> 04:22.980
we won't have to be submissive

04:22.980 --> 04:25.020
or be suppressed by other sects.

04:25.020 --> 04:26.100
That's right, young lady.

04:26.410 --> 04:28.140
I also admire Ms. Cai.

04:28.660 --> 04:30.100
Once the Method is perfected,

04:30.100 --> 04:31.850
we can go out to uphold justice.

04:32.250 --> 04:34.370
That would not disgrace Ms. Cai's name.

04:34.890 --> 04:35.730
Right?

04:35.730 --> 04:36.570
Zhao?

04:40.610 --> 04:41.700
That makes sense.

04:43.290 --> 04:44.490
It's not impossible.

04:46.930 --> 04:47.770
Here you go.

05:00.020 --> 05:01.170
You're still alive.

05:01.290 --> 05:02.980
Your lover is dead.

05:02.980 --> 05:04.850
Of course, I'm still alive.

05:06.980 --> 05:07.980
Uncle Jiu.

05:12.540 --> 05:13.810
You're a junior.

05:14.050 --> 05:15.390
I won't make things hard for you.

05:15.810 --> 05:17.100
Hand over the saliva,

05:17.410 --> 05:18.660
and you may leave.

05:20.140 --> 05:21.540
Saliva in exchange for my life.

05:21.980 --> 05:23.100
That's not a bad deal.

05:23.370 --> 05:24.810
But this saliva

05:25.580 --> 05:26.660
is only a little.

05:28.140 --> 05:30.340
Is it enough for the three of you?

05:33.370 --> 05:35.930
No matter which one of you I give it to,

05:36.170 --> 05:37.250
the other two

05:38.170 --> 05:40.370
will harbor hatred toward me

05:41.020 --> 05:42.700
and want me dead.

05:44.730 --> 05:46.250
Give it to me.

05:46.250 --> 05:48.410
They won't dare act rashly.

05:49.540 --> 05:50.410
I don't believe it.

05:51.490 --> 05:53.540
Unless you kill them all.

05:59.170 --> 06:00.010
No.

06:00.490 --> 06:01.980
What if you fake your deaths

06:02.610 --> 06:04.730
and escape?

06:05.170 --> 06:06.580
Wouldn't I suffer a huge loss?

06:07.410 --> 06:08.580
What do you want?

06:15.780 --> 06:18.220
I want you to cut off

06:24.020 --> 06:25.610
Zhou Zhiqin's head.

06:25.730 --> 06:27.370
When his head is separated
from his body,

06:27.580 --> 06:29.100
I will hand over the saliva.

06:29.410 --> 06:30.250
Cai Zhao,

06:30.540 --> 06:31.660
have you lost your mind?

06:32.050 --> 06:34.290
If not for you letting
that damned man escape,

06:34.290 --> 06:36.020
so many people wouldn't have died.

06:36.240 --> 06:38.060
Go to the underworld
and atone for your sins.

06:39.850 --> 06:40.690
Elder Duan,

06:41.410 --> 06:43.170
don't listen to her sowing discord.

06:44.410 --> 06:46.610
As expected

06:46.610 --> 06:48.140
of that vile Cai Pingshu,

06:48.660 --> 06:50.410
raising such a vicious little wretch.

06:50.850 --> 06:51.690
Fine.

06:52.540 --> 06:53.540
Since you say that,

06:54.170 --> 06:55.220
let's perish together.

06:55.300 --> 06:56.140
- Wait.
- No.

06:56.140 --> 06:57.220
Let's talk it out.

06:57.340 --> 06:58.490
Talk it out, huh?

06:58.850 --> 07:00.370
Then will you speak properly?

07:00.780 --> 07:01.980
From now on,

07:01.980 --> 07:03.290
I don't want to hear a single word

07:03.290 --> 07:05.100
disrespecting my aunt.

07:05.410 --> 07:06.660
Uncle Jiu was just anxious.

07:06.660 --> 07:08.340
He didn't mean to slight your aunt.

07:08.340 --> 07:09.540
We won't say it anymore.

07:09.540 --> 07:10.380
We won't.

07:13.700 --> 07:16.490
Stop putting on airs before me.

07:16.930 --> 07:18.370
If I'm unhappy,

07:18.490 --> 07:20.810
I can let go of the saliva,

07:21.020 --> 07:21.900
but you

07:22.980 --> 07:24.730
must die.

07:24.730 --> 07:25.660
Then die.

07:25.660 --> 07:26.500
No, no.

07:30.780 --> 07:32.700
Are you going to do it or not?

07:34.170 --> 07:35.490
I'll count to three.

07:35.780 --> 07:36.620
One.

07:37.850 --> 07:38.690
Two.

07:39.290 --> 07:40.140
Three!

07:40.140 --> 07:40.980
Fine.

07:43.930 --> 07:45.050
I agree.

07:47.290 --> 07:48.130
Uncle Jiu.

07:48.410 --> 07:49.370
Qinong,

07:50.410 --> 07:51.930
I'm old.

07:52.340 --> 07:53.730
I can't wait any longer.

07:54.660 --> 07:56.410
Don't blame me.

08:35.300 --> 08:36.220
Young lady,

08:36.490 --> 08:37.770
there's no way out.

08:38.300 --> 08:39.610
Hand over the saliva,

08:40.100 --> 08:41.370
and I'll let you go.

08:44.700 --> 08:45.540
Here you go.

08:50.820 --> 08:52.940
You wretch. I'll kill you.

09:05.850 --> 09:07.060
Why are you still here?

09:09.790 --> 09:10.650
Jerk!

09:10.650 --> 09:11.700
You're not dead?

09:12.300 --> 09:13.280
You were waiting for me.

09:13.610 --> 09:14.450
How would I dare die?

09:14.700 --> 09:15.540
Impossible.

09:15.700 --> 09:18.060
I saw you dragged away by the python.

09:18.340 --> 09:20.130
That's true.

09:20.730 --> 09:22.850
But the python hates heat.

09:23.250 --> 09:24.730
When my mindful way circulates,

09:24.730 --> 09:25.850
my whole body heats up.

09:26.130 --> 09:27.530
So, the python let me go.

09:28.010 --> 09:29.420
I was quite lucky.

09:30.130 --> 09:31.770
I even met a friend.

09:42.340 --> 09:43.300
Qian Xueshen?

09:48.490 --> 09:49.730
Weren't you already...

09:49.980 --> 09:52.060
He bribed Mr. Zhang
and swapped identities with him.

09:53.370 --> 09:55.010
The one who died there was Mr. Zhang.

09:55.650 --> 09:56.850
Normally, once a person dies,

09:57.060 --> 09:59.100
the Body Shift will end.

09:59.610 --> 10:01.180
But the corpse was destroyed at once.

10:01.730 --> 10:03.010
So, it was flawless,

10:03.340 --> 10:05.850
and his scheme succeeded.

10:09.300 --> 10:11.370
You also placed the statue

10:11.770 --> 10:13.180
of my ancestor Gu Qingkong?

10:15.610 --> 10:16.940
It's the Jade Statue.

10:20.530 --> 10:21.650
Were you trying

10:22.180 --> 10:23.580
to lure us into the ice cave

10:23.730 --> 10:25.010
to be attacked by the python?

10:28.530 --> 10:29.700
Why did you do this?

10:32.100 --> 10:33.580
Because this hunting lodge

10:34.700 --> 10:35.850
is my home.

10:39.580 --> 10:40.420
So,

10:40.940 --> 10:42.730
you are the son of that family.

10:43.340 --> 10:45.180
What was that hunter's surname again?

10:45.420 --> 10:48.130
I can't quite remember.

10:48.490 --> 10:49.330
Tao.

10:50.130 --> 10:51.610
If I remember correctly,

10:52.180 --> 10:54.730
that young wife was quite pretty.

10:54.730 --> 10:56.220
That was my aunt.

10:58.820 --> 11:00.770
She was even pregnant.

11:01.700 --> 11:03.010
Fifteen years ago,

11:03.180 --> 11:05.340
you should've long been buried
by the snow.

11:06.060 --> 11:07.770
It was my father and uncle

11:07.770 --> 11:09.530
who dug you out one by one

11:10.250 --> 11:11.890
and brought you home to recover.

11:13.010 --> 11:13.850
Hey, everyone.

11:13.850 --> 11:14.700
Come and help.

11:15.700 --> 11:17.020
- Here, Shu.
- Father.

11:17.820 --> 11:18.660
Come on.

11:20.610 --> 11:22.340
Some wandering martial folks

11:22.340 --> 11:23.473
were searching for treasure,

11:23.890 --> 11:26.370
using powder and causing an avalanche.

11:27.300 --> 11:29.530
Luckily, we heard the noise

11:29.530 --> 11:30.420
and dug them out.

11:30.730 --> 11:31.570
Their lives

11:31.770 --> 11:32.820
were barely saved.

11:33.490 --> 11:34.820
But the first thing

11:35.300 --> 11:37.180
you did after waking up

11:37.730 --> 11:40.770
was to silence them.

11:49.010 --> 11:50.300
You beasts.

11:50.300 --> 11:51.730
I'll kill you!

12:16.980 --> 12:18.490
My child is about to be born.

12:19.250 --> 12:20.700
Please let me go.

12:27.180 --> 12:29.220
In this barren, freezing land,

12:29.890 --> 12:31.490
you're so delicate and pretty.

12:31.700 --> 12:33.610
After all, they did save us.

12:33.980 --> 12:34.850
Why not

12:35.730 --> 12:37.220
let them die painlessly?

12:40.300 --> 12:41.580
What a surprise

12:41.580 --> 12:43.490
that you'd be so compassionate.

12:46.490 --> 12:48.580
How pretty and delicate.

12:49.220 --> 12:50.890
Don't worry. It won't hurt.

12:55.420 --> 12:56.260
What a sin.

12:56.980 --> 12:58.490
Stop pretending.

12:58.850 --> 13:00.220
Wasn't this your suggestion?

13:00.940 --> 13:03.580
"Though they weren't part of Jianghu,"

13:03.580 --> 13:05.770
"they often helped travelers."

13:05.770 --> 13:07.490
"If they said something"

13:07.490 --> 13:09.730
"and let people know
a righteous sect member"

13:10.220 --> 13:13.060
"like you were mingling with us,"

13:14.180 --> 13:16.420
"Qingque Sect wouldn't spare you."

13:16.730 --> 13:17.700
Now, you're pretending?

13:17.890 --> 13:18.770
Who is it for?

13:20.820 --> 13:23.820
If Nie Hengcheng were to learn

13:24.340 --> 13:27.100
that you colluded with Elder Duan
to secretly cultivate his skill,

13:28.340 --> 13:29.370
do you think

13:30.300 --> 13:31.820
he would spare you?

13:31.830 --> 13:32.670
What did you say?

13:32.670 --> 13:33.550
Enough.

13:33.770 --> 13:35.370
We're on the same side.

13:35.370 --> 13:36.300
Why argue about this?

13:37.060 --> 13:38.370
Let's hurry and find

13:38.370 --> 13:39.770
the saliva of the Snow-Scale Beast.

13:40.130 --> 13:40.970
Then

13:41.370 --> 13:43.220
what about these corpses?

13:46.250 --> 13:47.490
Burn them all.

13:48.180 --> 13:49.530
Save them from reincarnation.

14:09.700 --> 14:11.250
Failing to eradicate the roots

14:11.250 --> 14:12.940
surely brings endless trouble.

14:13.180 --> 14:14.020
Back then,

14:14.340 --> 14:16.770
we actually missed you.

14:17.060 --> 14:19.530
You were only 7 or 8 years.

14:19.770 --> 14:20.850
Alone in the snowfields,

14:20.850 --> 14:22.250
how did you survive until now?

14:22.490 --> 14:24.220
I met my master, Master Qianmian.

14:24.490 --> 14:25.770
He rescued me

14:26.220 --> 14:27.580
and taught me all my skills.

14:29.130 --> 14:30.580
After my master died,

14:32.100 --> 14:33.890
I returned here.

15:46.340 --> 15:47.220
Eat, Snow.

15:47.490 --> 15:49.300
I'll go steal some cured meat tonight.

15:49.300 --> 15:50.686
I'll come feed you again tomorrow.

16:15.890 --> 16:16.770
Snow,

16:17.010 --> 16:18.420
you've grown so big already.

16:28.539 --> 16:30.530
I spread news everywhere
that the Snow-Scale Beast

16:30.530 --> 16:32.010
had reappeared in the snow mountains,

16:32.580 --> 16:34.060
luring the greedy ones here,

16:35.130 --> 16:37.130
and then trapped them in the ice cave.

16:42.260 --> 16:45.380
(Zhou Yulin, Peiqiong Manor)

16:52.250 --> 16:56.610
You killed so many innocent people
for the saliva

16:56.610 --> 16:58.610
and even caused the death of your son.

16:58.610 --> 17:00.250
Even if you master
peerless martial arts,

17:00.370 --> 17:01.370
what use is it?

17:03.010 --> 17:05.180
I've always tried to lure you all here.

17:05.700 --> 17:07.700
Unfortunately,
my identity was exposed midway

17:07.711 --> 17:09.239
and I was captured by the demonic sect.

17:09.250 --> 17:10.980
But heaven has eyes.

17:12.250 --> 17:13.380
Miss Cai

17:13.700 --> 17:15.620
brought me back here,

17:15.860 --> 17:19.660
and I finally met the enemies.

17:20.220 --> 17:22.490
I deliberately put the saliva
in your son's hands

17:22.900 --> 17:24.980
to make you kill each other.

17:29.700 --> 17:31.010
The saliva is yours?

17:31.010 --> 17:31.860
That's right.

17:32.700 --> 17:35.180
The Snow-Scale Beast did appear here.

17:35.660 --> 17:36.940
When I was little,

17:37.163 --> 17:38.810
my father and uncle collected
quite a bit

17:38.810 --> 17:40.530
of the saliva that dripped
onto the ground.

17:41.010 --> 17:43.050
Do you remember the bed you slept on?

17:43.250 --> 17:44.900
Fifteen years ago,

17:44.900 --> 17:46.700
the saliva of the Snow-Scale Beast

17:47.420 --> 17:49.940
was in the ice chest under the bed.

17:50.420 --> 17:52.620
You didn't have to wait for 15 years.

17:54.620 --> 17:56.330
Take out the remaining slime.

17:56.730 --> 17:58.860
The last beast is already dead.

17:59.660 --> 18:01.380
What Miss Cai poured out just now

18:02.050 --> 18:04.860
was indeed the last saliva in the world.

18:05.940 --> 18:06.940
You're lying.

18:07.940 --> 18:09.490
There must still be saliva.

18:09.770 --> 18:11.620
Take out the remaining slime.

18:11.620 --> 18:12.460
Don't.

18:12.570 --> 18:13.590
My wounds haven't healed.

18:13.660 --> 18:14.500
I can't win.

18:14.886 --> 18:16.730
- We'll find a chance to leave.
- Take it out.

18:16.730 --> 18:18.180
- Leave him to later.
- Take it out.

18:18.180 --> 18:19.220
Take it out.

18:23.810 --> 18:24.660
What is this?

18:24.980 --> 18:27.010
This is gland fluid I extracted
from the bodies

18:27.010 --> 18:28.420
of a thousand female snakes.

18:28.730 --> 18:30.250
Once male snakes smell it, they go mad.

18:30.570 --> 18:31.700
No matter where you flee,

18:31.700 --> 18:32.980
they will devour you

18:35.140 --> 18:36.700
until death.

18:51.620 --> 18:52.460
Qinong.

18:52.700 --> 18:54.620
Come and help me.

18:55.330 --> 18:56.180
Qinong.

19:01.530 --> 19:02.370
Qian Xueshen!

19:30.770 --> 19:32.140
I have the Ziwei Method.

19:32.250 --> 19:33.380
I have the Ziwei Method.

19:33.380 --> 19:34.220
Tell me.

19:34.330 --> 19:35.980
Has Nie Zhe's Wudu Palm been perfected?

19:36.770 --> 19:38.010
It's you.

19:38.250 --> 19:39.620
Go, Qian Xueshen.

19:39.620 --> 19:41.090
Why save me?

19:41.940 --> 19:43.050
You're not a bad person.

19:43.290 --> 19:44.250
You shouldn't die.

19:44.250 --> 19:45.420
I'm not a bad person?

19:45.660 --> 19:46.860
Are you blind?

19:47.730 --> 19:49.140
I wanted to die long ago.

19:49.490 --> 19:50.330
Qian Xueshen,

19:50.383 --> 19:51.860
your whole family is dead except you.

19:51.936 --> 19:53.763
When you reunite
with them in the underworld,

19:53.774 --> 19:55.294
your parents will surely be delighted.

20:03.660 --> 20:04.620
Mu Qingyan!

20:04.620 --> 20:06.250
The avalanche! Run!

20:50.490 --> 20:51.330
Zhao.

20:57.420 --> 20:58.260
Zhao.

21:30.810 --> 21:32.090
Where is this?

21:34.980 --> 21:35.980
Where is Qian Xueshen?

21:39.490 --> 21:41.730
Once you woke up, you asked about him.

21:43.513 --> 21:45.180
Why don't you think
about how to repay me?

21:45.940 --> 21:47.050
I have no money.

21:47.860 --> 21:48.700
Just my life.

21:55.940 --> 21:57.940
Even if you ask me
to give myself to you,

21:57.986 --> 21:59.330
at most it's one night of passion.

21:59.546 --> 22:01.090
I won't take responsibility afterward.

22:07.060 --> 22:08.740
♪In days gone by♪

22:08.770 --> 22:09.610
It's fine.

22:10.950 --> 22:13.700
♪I first saw you in the dimness♪

22:14.670 --> 22:15.860
♪Amid the vast crowd♪

22:15.870 --> 22:17.340
♪A fleeting glance♪

22:17.510 --> 22:18.420
♪And then♪

22:19.860 --> 22:21.380
One night of passion

22:22.140 --> 22:23.620
is better than tasting

22:23.860 --> 22:25.050
no sweetness at all.

22:26.040 --> 22:27.380
♪Alas, we parted♪

22:27.390 --> 22:29.580
♪Longing for your return♪

22:29.710 --> 22:30.660
♪Moon waxes and wanes♪

22:30.670 --> 22:32.140
♪Letters can't convey my thoughts♪

22:32.150 --> 22:33.180
♪Scattered petals♪

22:33.190 --> 22:35.420
♪Cover the ground♪

22:36.480 --> 22:38.740
♪Such should be our meeting♪

22:38.940 --> 22:43.610
♪Golden wind brushes the jade dew♪

22:43.620 --> 22:46.340
♪Half shy, half joyful♪

22:46.550 --> 22:50.430
♪Wanting to leave yet lingering♪

22:51.220 --> 22:53.790
♪Such should be our meeting♪

22:53.970 --> 22:58.320
♪Across the Magpie Bridge♪

22:58.650 --> 23:01.200
♪Alas, peach blossoms have fallen♪

23:01.440 --> 23:07.320
♪Tears are like pearls♪

23:23.616 --> 23:25.570
The tri-colored peach blossoms
of Luoying Valley.

23:25.690 --> 23:27.140
So, this place has quite a connection

23:27.140 --> 23:29.140
with your Luoying Valley.

23:30.250 --> 23:31.090
You're awake.

23:33.290 --> 23:34.660
The landlady?

23:39.490 --> 23:41.900
It must have been you two who saved us.

23:42.050 --> 23:44.490
You soaked in the Wanzai Hot Spring
for quite some time.

23:44.636 --> 23:45.660
Your injuries have healed.

23:45.660 --> 23:47.570
Only one of his poisons
remains hard to remove.

23:47.980 --> 23:49.180
Thank you.

23:50.140 --> 23:50.980
Sit.

23:58.860 --> 23:59.700
Senior,

24:00.373 --> 24:01.260
where is Qian Xueshen?

24:01.480 --> 24:02.330
Is he all right?

24:02.330 --> 24:03.730
He's much sturdier than you.

24:04.050 --> 24:05.290
He woke up yesterday.

24:11.180 --> 24:12.730
Why is that pretty boy

24:13.490 --> 24:14.730
still alive?

24:15.810 --> 24:17.570
This is the pattern of Luoying Valley.

24:18.940 --> 24:19.980
Senior, are you

24:20.700 --> 24:23.090
a descendant of my ancestor,
Ms. Gu Qingkong?

24:27.140 --> 24:29.180
This is my master's grandmaster,

24:29.980 --> 24:31.700
your ancestor, Gu Qingkong,

24:32.940 --> 24:33.780
Ms. Gu.

24:35.490 --> 24:36.490
200 years ago,

24:36.501 --> 24:38.999
Founder Beichen summoned spirit beasts
from the immortal realm

24:39.010 --> 24:40.140
to eradicate demons.

24:40.423 --> 24:43.320
Later, martial practitioners discovered
that spirit beasts were helpful.

24:43.570 --> 24:44.620
They forgot gratitude

24:44.620 --> 24:45.860
and slaughtered them wantonly.

24:46.620 --> 24:48.250
Ms. Gu, to protect the spirit beasts,

24:48.900 --> 24:50.770
stood against all martial practitioners.

24:51.140 --> 24:52.810
But no matter how gifted she was,

24:53.050 --> 24:55.050
she could not withstand
endless human greed.

24:56.010 --> 24:56.850
In the end,

24:57.180 --> 24:59.620
she could only flee here
with the surviving spirit beasts

25:01.220 --> 25:02.620
and vanish without a trace.

25:03.180 --> 25:04.940
That's our first demoness.

25:05.090 --> 25:06.010
Independent

25:06.250 --> 25:07.180
and exceptional.

25:07.570 --> 25:10.010
They say your demonesses defy the world

25:10.010 --> 25:11.180
and are intolerable to all.

25:11.330 --> 25:12.770
Why are you so proud about it?

25:13.140 --> 25:15.090
They were smeared
because they were invincible.

25:15.660 --> 25:16.500
No need to mind it.

25:17.860 --> 25:18.700
Zhao is right.

25:19.770 --> 25:22.660
Those people are simply shameless.

25:24.900 --> 25:25.810
By the way, senior,

25:25.810 --> 25:27.050
does the Snow-Scale Beast

25:28.010 --> 25:30.140
still live today?

25:30.570 --> 25:32.010
When your aunt came back then,

25:32.420 --> 25:36.090
the last Snow-Scale Beast
was already at death's door.

25:36.290 --> 25:37.180
My aunt came here?

25:38.700 --> 25:40.250
She also came to look for the saliva.

25:41.330 --> 25:44.290
A masked man traveled with her.

25:44.770 --> 25:47.730
This painting was drawn by that man.

25:51.490 --> 25:53.940
(Uncle Zhou and Master are upright.)

25:54.050 --> 25:55.330
(They shouldn't have worn masks.)

25:56.980 --> 25:59.010
Why did my aunt seek the saliva,

25:59.010 --> 26:00.250
and who was that man?

26:00.730 --> 26:03.660
Have you known Qian Xueshen
for a long time?

26:04.330 --> 26:07.620
The Tao family often brought prey
to my master and me.

26:08.050 --> 26:09.770
Shu and I grew up together.

26:09.993 --> 26:11.380
The inn at the foot of the mountain

26:11.660 --> 26:13.700
was set up to avenge the Tao family.

26:14.010 --> 26:15.860
First, to gather information.

26:16.420 --> 26:17.260
Second,

26:17.620 --> 26:20.490
to stop innocent people
from dying senselessly.

26:20.940 --> 26:23.140
Since you were so close
to the Tao family,

26:23.700 --> 26:24.540
then

26:24.900 --> 26:26.620
why didn't you intervene

26:27.140 --> 26:28.810
the night they were killed?

26:33.010 --> 26:33.850
At that time,

26:34.220 --> 26:36.980
I was away seeking spirit medicine
for the dying Snow-Scale Beast.

26:37.530 --> 26:38.660
I wasn't on the mountain.

26:39.220 --> 26:40.810
The Tao family were all kind people

26:41.290 --> 26:42.900
and saved many travelers.

26:43.330 --> 26:44.490
Who could have expected

26:45.010 --> 26:46.090
that this world

26:47.090 --> 26:48.220
and the people of Jianghu

26:49.250 --> 26:50.490
had never changed?

26:51.700 --> 26:52.770
Where is Qian Xueshen?

26:58.570 --> 26:59.420
Qian Xueshen.

27:01.140 --> 27:02.420
My name is not Qian Xueshen.

27:05.180 --> 27:06.250
My name is Tao Shu.

27:06.620 --> 27:07.460
Miss Cai.

27:08.050 --> 27:08.890
Mr. Mu.

27:09.180 --> 27:10.693
Thank you for helping me avenge them.

27:10.900 --> 27:12.090
No need to thank us.

27:12.420 --> 27:13.260
In the end,

27:13.420 --> 27:15.180
all sects owe you a debt.

27:16.900 --> 27:17.740
Qian...

27:18.290 --> 27:19.130
Shu,

27:20.250 --> 27:21.860
is there still even a little

27:22.140 --> 27:23.620
of the Snow-Scale Beast's saliva left?

27:25.330 --> 27:26.660
Has the Snow-Scale Beast

27:26.980 --> 27:28.700
left behind

27:29.180 --> 27:30.020
anything else?

27:31.860 --> 27:33.010
Xuegu once said

27:33.940 --> 27:35.860
the Snow-Scale Beast
seemed to have left an egg.

27:42.420 --> 27:44.730
A Snow-Scale Beast lays eggs?

27:46.810 --> 27:49.090
Ancient dragons reproduce by eggs.

27:49.420 --> 27:51.090
But this egg has been laid
for many years

27:51.290 --> 27:52.420
and still refuses to hatch.

27:52.810 --> 27:54.180
Didn't you raise Peng birds before?

27:54.285 --> 27:55.792
You should know how to incubate eggs.

27:56.090 --> 27:58.290
Call over your two Golden Pengs
to hatch it.

27:58.530 --> 27:59.660
My Golden Pengs are male.

28:00.250 --> 28:01.220
Both of them?

28:02.250 --> 28:03.330
That's too cruel of you.

28:03.330 --> 28:04.250
I...

28:04.250 --> 28:06.420
Peng birds and dragon beasts
are natural enemies.

28:06.464 --> 28:07.969
Dragon beasts are spiritual creatures.

28:07.980 --> 28:08.940
If they sense danger,

28:09.140 --> 28:10.220
they will never hatch.

28:10.730 --> 28:12.250
Using Peng birds won't work.

28:13.220 --> 28:14.380
My father once said

28:15.730 --> 28:18.290
that ancient spirit beasts resonate
with their masters.

28:18.530 --> 28:20.980
They rely on recognizing blood aura

28:21.660 --> 28:22.730
to form a bond.

28:23.290 --> 28:24.660
Since this Snow-Scale Beast

28:25.050 --> 28:26.900
was saved by Luoying Valley's ancestor,

28:27.330 --> 28:28.756
and they'd lived together for years,

28:29.140 --> 28:30.810
it must recognize that blood aura.

28:32.250 --> 28:33.220
Perhaps

28:35.420 --> 28:37.090
the blood aura of Luoying Valley

28:38.330 --> 28:39.570
can awaken it.

28:54.090 --> 28:55.140
Did your father say

28:55.380 --> 28:57.380
how much blood is needed
to raise a spirit beast?

28:57.570 --> 28:58.860
I've been weak in blood aura.

28:58.860 --> 29:00.250
I don't know if it'll work.

29:12.330 --> 29:13.170
Look.

29:13.490 --> 29:14.330
It didn't work.

29:15.380 --> 29:16.380
That shouldn't be.

29:17.530 --> 29:18.370
Again.

29:25.050 --> 29:25.940
Mu Qingyan!

29:25.940 --> 29:26.780
Look.

29:51.530 --> 29:53.250
Dragon.

30:00.380 --> 30:01.660
So good.

30:03.420 --> 30:04.260
Dragon.

30:04.730 --> 30:06.420
Spit out some saliva.

30:10.330 --> 30:11.380
You've got nerve.

30:12.490 --> 30:13.490
Come on.

30:13.501 --> 30:14.660
If you don't spit out saliva,

30:14.660 --> 30:15.683
I'll stew you into soup.

30:23.180 --> 30:24.020
Get down here.

30:26.290 --> 30:27.196
If you don't come down,

30:27.420 --> 30:28.330
I'll braise you.

30:31.050 --> 30:31.890
Don't run.

30:33.490 --> 30:34.380
Don't run.

30:36.380 --> 30:37.373
I'll chop you into mince

30:37.570 --> 30:38.410
and make wonton.

30:54.700 --> 30:56.620
Give me some.

30:56.620 --> 30:58.330
Please.

31:01.140 --> 31:02.330
Come on.

31:12.010 --> 31:12.980
I'm telling you.

31:13.700 --> 31:15.140
Behave,

31:15.530 --> 31:16.860
or I'll kill you.

31:28.420 --> 31:30.570
(Isn't this Grandfather's mechanism?)

31:33.330 --> 31:34.290
It fell asleep.

31:35.380 --> 31:36.900
So cute.

31:39.530 --> 31:41.860
Once I get the saliva
and find my master,

31:41.980 --> 31:43.420
I'll come back to keep it company.

31:46.980 --> 31:48.770
You complain for three days

31:48.939 --> 31:50.512
just because a wonton has no scallions.

31:50.730 --> 31:53.220
Someone so attached to worldly pleasures

31:54.010 --> 31:56.530
could hardly last three days

31:57.770 --> 31:58.980
on this cold, silent snow peak.

31:59.450 --> 32:00.900
And you want to live here long-term?

32:02.980 --> 32:04.330
Why say it out loud?

32:11.220 --> 32:12.900
I selfishly forced it

32:13.570 --> 32:15.290
to hatch.

32:16.090 --> 32:19.770
There's only one Snow-Scale Beast
in this world.

32:20.380 --> 32:21.730
It must be very lonely.

32:22.490 --> 32:24.380
The Snow-Scale Beast
lives a very long life.

32:24.700 --> 32:26.730
At least 200 years.

32:27.010 --> 32:28.936
In 200 years, the world
will change many times.

32:29.220 --> 32:30.730
Maybe somewhere out there,

32:31.010 --> 32:32.770
another of its kind will appear.

32:32.980 --> 32:33.820
So,

32:34.730 --> 32:36.090
we ordinary mortals

32:37.050 --> 32:38.490
needn't rack our brains worrying

32:38.770 --> 32:41.660
about this long-lived little creature.

32:44.900 --> 32:47.010
You seem pretty concerned yourself.

32:47.140 --> 32:48.770
How would I care

32:49.490 --> 32:51.700
about a little spirit beast?

32:52.050 --> 32:52.890
Really?

33:05.250 --> 33:06.380
Hard work pays off.

33:06.700 --> 33:07.810
We finally got it.

33:15.660 --> 33:16.810
But can this thing

33:18.050 --> 33:20.050
really counter the Body Shift?

33:26.980 --> 33:27.820
Don't move.

33:35.090 --> 33:35.940
Young Master,

33:36.420 --> 33:37.260
forgive me.

33:57.570 --> 33:59.140
Why turn me into a woman?

34:09.740 --> 34:11.260
After taking the saliva,

34:11.260 --> 34:12.666
it takes two hours to take effect.

34:14.610 --> 34:15.940
What if I can't change back?

34:15.940 --> 34:16.860
Rest assured.

34:16.860 --> 34:17.700
You will.

34:18.260 --> 34:20.050
I have something to do. I'll go first.

34:23.740 --> 34:25.780
Anyway, the antidote takes two hours.

34:25.940 --> 34:27.082
Since you have nothing to do,

34:27.093 --> 34:28.013
do me a favor.

34:28.210 --> 34:29.780
Whatever is in your mind,

34:30.170 --> 34:31.090
it's impossible.

34:31.090 --> 34:32.570
Mu.

34:33.130 --> 34:36.010
I even borrowed these clothes for you.

34:52.050 --> 34:53.010
Xuegu?

34:53.530 --> 34:54.370
Senior,

34:55.130 --> 34:56.650
Xuegu wants to ask you

34:56.940 --> 34:58.570
why you hid your identity from her.

34:58.980 --> 35:00.420
Qian Xueshen said you have no name

35:00.420 --> 35:01.300
and belong to no sect.

35:01.650 --> 35:03.530
Why do you know
the Ning clan's mechanisms?

35:04.010 --> 35:04.850
Could it be...

35:04.860 --> 35:05.740
Is your mother well?

35:06.210 --> 35:07.050
Uncle?

35:07.900 --> 35:09.650
My mother said
you disappeared 15 years ago.

35:09.860 --> 35:11.260
Everyone thought you were dead.

35:11.610 --> 35:12.940
I have been reborn.

35:13.090 --> 35:14.210
The past

35:14.210 --> 35:15.170
no longer counts.

35:16.860 --> 35:17.700
Mr. Mu.

35:18.530 --> 35:21.050
Is this the Qianmian Sect's Body Shift?

35:22.340 --> 35:23.180
Uncle,

35:23.300 --> 35:25.130
you even recognized him?

35:25.130 --> 35:27.249
Xuegu and I have known each other
for over ten years.

35:27.260 --> 35:29.210
I can tell at a glance.

35:29.490 --> 35:31.050
Mr. Ning, sharp eyes indeed.

35:31.820 --> 35:32.660
Uncle,

35:32.940 --> 35:35.490
my mother and great-aunt
often think of you.

35:35.740 --> 35:37.010
When do you plan to return?

35:41.010 --> 35:41.850
I won't.

35:42.130 --> 35:43.340
The world is dull.

35:43.490 --> 35:45.010
My beloved matters more.

35:45.910 --> 35:46.980
Xuegu is about to wake up.

35:47.210 --> 35:49.820
I need to brew tea
and cook congee for her.

35:59.900 --> 36:01.300
It really works.

36:02.210 --> 36:03.130
We can go back.

36:03.130 --> 36:04.530
We'll depart early tomorrow morning.

36:05.210 --> 36:06.340
Uncle warned me

36:06.690 --> 36:08.610
not to reveal the snow mountains
or his matters,

36:09.610 --> 36:12.530
so the spirit beasts and they
can have their last pure land.

36:14.420 --> 36:15.610
Once we part,

36:18.050 --> 36:20.690
I don't think we'll meet again.

36:24.690 --> 36:25.530
Zhao,

36:27.570 --> 36:29.010
would you give up everything

36:30.380 --> 36:31.530
for the one you love?

36:36.340 --> 36:37.300
Of course not.

36:37.860 --> 36:38.700
As you said,

36:38.820 --> 36:40.420
I'm attached to the bustling world.

36:40.860 --> 36:41.700
Besides,

36:41.940 --> 36:43.233
I haven't become the Manager yet.

36:43.740 --> 36:45.480
How could I give up everything
for someone?

36:46.780 --> 36:47.980
What if it were for me?

36:48.690 --> 36:49.530
For you?

36:53.300 --> 36:54.340
I'd be even less willing.

36:54.900 --> 36:55.820
Think about it.

36:55.820 --> 36:58.260
The Lord of Qianmian Sect
made a wrong choice

36:58.610 --> 37:00.780
and ruined the entire sect.

37:01.090 --> 37:02.860
The past warns the future.

37:03.650 --> 37:05.130
I wouldn't do something that foolish.

37:07.610 --> 37:08.610
You're right.

37:10.300 --> 37:11.140
What about you?

37:13.130 --> 37:14.900
Would you give up everything
for someone?

37:15.340 --> 37:16.180
I would.

37:17.010 --> 37:17.850
I don't believe it.

37:18.570 --> 37:19.900
There's nothing I can't give up.

37:21.300 --> 37:22.980
As the Young Master,

37:23.170 --> 37:25.170
you'll surely have
piles of gold and silver,

37:25.170 --> 37:26.300
wives and concubines aplenty,

37:26.300 --> 37:27.530
fine clothes, and rich food.

37:27.690 --> 37:29.690
You have everything to give up,

37:30.050 --> 37:31.490
but you just can't.

37:32.050 --> 37:33.780
Is that how you see the life

37:34.130 --> 37:35.050
of the Young Master?

37:35.490 --> 37:36.330
Then what is it like?

37:59.650 --> 38:00.610
What a lousy bird,

38:00.610 --> 38:01.780
wanting to eat a little beast.

38:04.130 --> 38:05.340
They're natural enemies,

38:06.573 --> 38:07.690
locked in deadly opposition

38:07.690 --> 38:09.900
for generations.

38:09.900 --> 38:10.740
Just like the Li Sect

38:10.740 --> 38:12.210
and your Six Sects.

38:13.940 --> 38:15.780
As long as you're happy.

38:19.090 --> 38:20.650
You really aren't coming with us?

38:21.010 --> 38:23.260
This frozen wilderness is deserted.

38:23.820 --> 38:25.050
My uncle stayed for Xuegu.

38:25.210 --> 38:26.300
Why are you staying?

38:26.490 --> 38:27.330
For it.

38:31.900 --> 38:33.090
The Snow-Scale Beast

38:33.490 --> 38:34.610
or the Body Shift

38:35.210 --> 38:36.936
never should have reappeared
in this world.

38:37.820 --> 38:39.380
I couldn't let go of this skin.

38:39.569 --> 38:41.455
Consider me leaving an heir
for the Tao family.

38:43.050 --> 38:45.130
This is where my family
lived for generations.

38:45.610 --> 38:46.650
Staying here,

38:47.420 --> 38:48.420
I feel at ease.

38:48.980 --> 38:50.570
I'll raise the little dragon beast.

38:52.210 --> 38:53.090
Ms. Cai.

38:53.260 --> 38:54.100
Mr. Mu.

38:54.570 --> 38:56.740
Meeting you both was my fortune.

38:57.210 --> 38:58.860
All banquets must end.

38:58.980 --> 38:59.820
Let us

39:00.210 --> 39:01.340
part here.

39:02.380 --> 39:03.220
Take care.

39:03.530 --> 39:04.320
Take care.

39:04.420 --> 39:05.260
Take care.

39:12.570 --> 39:13.860
(May we never meet again.)

39:15.490 --> 39:16.330
(Zhao,)

39:17.130 --> 39:18.050
(thank you.)

39:19.530 --> 39:20.780
(Thank you for believing in me)

39:21.690 --> 39:24.300
(and not giving up on me.)

39:53.610 --> 39:54.690
Come and help.

40:01.610 --> 40:02.490
People

40:02.490 --> 40:03.940
are both good and bad.

40:04.820 --> 40:07.010
Even if you save just one good person,

40:07.300 --> 40:08.340
it's worth it.

40:08.730 --> 40:09.570
Do you understand?

40:09.570 --> 40:10.610
Mother.

40:12.340 --> 40:14.260
Father. Mother.

40:15.570 --> 40:17.690
If I encounter travelers in need again,

40:18.210 --> 40:20.740
I will still save them,
just like you did.

40:22.420 --> 40:24.050
You were never wrong.

40:24.780 --> 40:26.820
Those who do evil are.

40:36.601 --> 40:47.261
=Generation to Generation=

41:06.021 --> 41:10.431
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

41:10.996 --> 41:15.611
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

41:15.951 --> 41:20.516
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

41:21.041 --> 41:25.341
♪Free to wander in the world♪

41:28.286 --> 41:32.986
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

41:33.511 --> 41:37.801
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

41:38.461 --> 41:42.491
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

41:42.806 --> 41:47.931
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

41:48.506 --> 41:53.316
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

41:53.531 --> 41:57.701
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

41:58.426 --> 42:02.361
♪I freely roam in the world♪

42:02.861 --> 42:08.136
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

42:30.866 --> 42:35.996
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

42:36.361 --> 42:40.731
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

42:40.996 --> 42:45.126
♪I freely roam in the world♪

42:45.311 --> 42:50.886
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
